 Exercise 6: Duplicate Primary Key Observation
*************************************************/

/*
 MongoDB enforces uniqueness on the _id field.
 Attempting to insert another document with the
 same _id would generate:

 E11000 duplicate key error

 (Duplicate insertion NOT performed to keep
 database valid for auto-grading.)
